column1:
Contains Duplicate
Given an integer array nums, return true if any value appears at least twice in the array, and return false if every element is distinct.
column2: Add chars to HashSet while iterating. If already present, return True

column1:
Valid Anagram
Given two strings s and t, return true if t is an anagram of s, and false otherwise.
column2: If lengths of s and t are not same, return False. Use counter(HashMap) to track character frequencies by incrementing for characters in s and decrementing for those in t. if any counts are not zero, return False; otherwise, return True
